<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>A Cleaner and Better Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>A Cleaner and Better Website</h1>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section>
            <p>This is a cleaner, minimalist version of a simple website.</p>
            <p>It uses Times New Roman, a classic serif font, for a professional look.</p>
            <p>The layout is responsive, ensuring readability on any device.</p>
            <p>No unnecessary elements, just the content you need.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Why Minimalism?</h2>
            <p>Minimalism in web design ensures that the content is the focus, free from distractions.</p>
            <p>It also enhances loading speeds and improves user experience.</p>
            <p>This website is an example of how clean design can be effective and elegant.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 A Cleaner and Better Website</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
